declare function abacus-xq-fn:LookupDVM($DVMName as xs:string,
                              $SourceName as xs:string,
                              $SourceValue as xs:string,
                              $TargetName as xs:string,
                              $DefaultValue as xs:string) as xs:string external;

declare function xf:RegionName($GLOBAL_BU_ID as xs:string)
    as xs:string {      
      if($GLOBAL_BU_ID != '') then 
    	let $intGLOBAL_BU_ID := xs:int($GLOBAL_BU_ID)
		return   
		    if($intGLOBAL_BU_ID = (1401,4081,8270,4075,4042,7465,7460,1717,4545,4046,4065,1313,4444,1841,8242,439,270)) then
				'AP'
			else if($intGLOBAL_BU_ID = 3535)  then
				'JP'
			else if( $intGLOBAL_BU_ID =(5959,3838,2828,2727,5458,3434,808,1224,5455,1919,1222,909,202,5000,552,5102,572,6161,531,2121,2323,3131,2929,546,584,1212,592,551,547,6969,5870,5065)) then
				'EMEA'		
				else if( $intGLOBAL_BU_ID =(11)) then
				'US'


			else($GLOBAL_BU_ID)
	 else ($GLOBAL_BU_ID)
};

declare function  xf:GetAdjustedTimeZone($SourceDate as xs:string, $OffSet as xs:string)
as xs:dateTime {
if(fn:substring($SourceDate,20,6)!='')then 
( fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xs:dateTime($SourceDate), xs:dayTimeDuration($OffSet)))
else
( fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xs:dateTime($SourceDate),xs:dayTimeDuration('PT0H')) , xs:dayTimeDuration($OffSet)))
};

declare function  xf:TimeZoneConversion($SourceDate as xs:string, $OffSet as xs:string)
as xs:dateTime {
let $Date :=  xf:GetAdjustedTimeZone($SourceDate,$OffSet)
return
xs:dateTime($Date)

};

declare function xf:SkuCurrencyConvert ($TransectionCurrencyCode as xs:string,
                                     $SkuCurrencyCode as xs:string,
                                     $SkuCost as xs:decimal,
                                     $USD_To_SellingCurrencyRate as xs:string,
                                     $USD_To_LocalCurrencyRate as xs:string
                                     )
as xs:decimal {

                if ($SkuCurrencyCode!='')then
                  (  
                     if($SkuCurrencyCode = $TransectionCurrencyCode)then
<ns1:SkuCost>{(xs:decimal(data($SkuCost)))}</ns1:SkuCost>

                   else if ($USD_To_LocalCurrencyRate!='' and xs:decimal(data($USD_To_LocalCurrencyRate))!=0 and  $SkuCurrencyCode!='USD' and $TransectionCurrencyCode='USD')then
<ns1:SkuCost>{(xs:decimal(data($SkuCost))) div (xs:decimal(data($USD_To_LocalCurrencyRate)))}</ns1:SkuCost> 

                    else if  ($USD_To_SellingCurrencyRate!='' and xs:decimal(data($USD_To_SellingCurrencyRate))!=0 and  $TransectionCurrencyCode!='USD' and $SkuCurrencyCode='USD') then
<ns1:SkuCost>{((xs:decimal(data($SkuCost)))* (xs:decimal(data($USD_To_SellingCurrencyRate))))} </ns1:SkuCost> 

                    else if ($USD_To_LocalCurrencyRate!='' and xs:decimal(data($USD_To_LocalCurrencyRate))!=0 and $USD_To_SellingCurrencyRate!='' and xs:decimal(data($USD_To_SellingCurrencyRate))!=0 ) then
<ns1:SkuCost>{(((xs:decimal(data($SkuCost))) div (xs:decimal(data($USD_To_LocalCurrencyRate)))* (xs:decimal(data($USD_To_SellingCurrencyRate)))))} </ns1:SkuCost> 

                    else(<ns1:SkuCost>0</ns1:SkuCost>)

                   )                     
                 else()
};

declare function xf:MonthConversion($MONTH as xs:string)
as xs:string {
let $MON:=xs:string(fn:upper-case($MONTH))
return
if ($MON = 'JAN') then '01'
else if ($MON = 'FEB') then '02'
else if ($MON = 'MAR') then '03'
else if ($MON = 'APR') then '04'
else if ($MON = 'MAY') then '05'
else if ($MON = 'JUN') then '06'
else if ($MON = 'JUL') then '07'
else if ($MON = 'AUG') then '08'
else if ($MON = 'SEP') then '09'
else if ($MON = 'OCT') then '10'
else if ($MON = 'NOV') then '11'
else if ($MON = 'DEC') then '12'
else ()
};

declare function xf:XformPublishSalesOrderEBMToSODSPublishSalesOrderABM($publishSalesOrderEBM1 as element(ns10:PublishSalesOrderEBM))
    as element(ns0:CreateSODSOrder) {
        <ns0:CreateSODSOrder MessageType = "CREATE">
            
{
let $TransectionCurrencyCode := data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:CurrencyCode)
            	 let $USDtoLocalCurrencyRate:= data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:USDtoLocalCurrencyRate)
                 let $USDtoSellingCurrencyRate:= data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:USDtoSellingCurrencyRate)

let $SalesOrderLine :=    for $salesorderline at $seq in  $publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine[ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemManufacturingCharacteristics/ns8:ConfiguratorModelTypeCode ='STANDARD'][ns10:Custom/ns3:Cancelled_Flag='N'][ns10:Custom/ns3:IsFreightSKU='N']
						return
						<ns10:OrderLine>
						<ns10:seq>{$seq}</ns10:seq>,
						<ns10:SalesOrderLine>{ $salesorderline/*}</ns10:SalesOrderLine>
						</ns10:OrderLine>
return
            	<ns0:CreateOrder>
                <ns0:SalesOrder ORDER_NUM = "{ if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderSource)!= "DM: SO Migration")then
                                                (data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_NUMBER']))
                                                else
                                                (data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGIN_SYSTEM_REFERENCE'])) }"
                                    ORDER_BUID = "{ data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID']) }"
                                    SOURCE_SYSTEM = "{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderSource)}"
                                     DPID = "{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='IRN_NUMBER'])}"
				    REBOOKED_ORDER_NUM="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUMBER'])}"
				    GII_BOOKING_REF_NUM ="{ if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:TypeName)="DM: SO Migration")then
                                                (data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_NUMBER']))
                                                else
                                                (data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGIN_SYSTEM_REFERENCE'])) }"
				    ASSOC_ORDER_BUID= ""
				    ASSOC_ORDER_NUM =""
				    MODIFIED_BY =""
				    MODIFIED_DATE =""
				    PO_NUM ="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:CustomerPurchaseOrderReference/ns6:Identification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='PURCHASE_ORDER_NUMBER'])}"
				    CONFIG_ID=""
				    SET_ID =""
				    ROUTING_INFO =""
				    SUPPLIER_NAME =""
				    RUSH_FLAG=""
				    SOFTWARE_CODE =""
				    MFG_ORDER_NUM =""
				    MFG_HOLD =""
				    CFI_NUM="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine[ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemManufacturingCharacteristics/ns8:ConfiguratorModelTypeCode ='STANDARD'][ns10:Custom/ns3:Cancelled_Flag='N'][ns10:Custom/ns3:IsFreightSKU='N'][1]/ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Custom/ns9:SystemIntegratorIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='SI_NUMBER'])}"
				    ODM_LOC=""
				    IN_PROD_DATE=""
				    HOLD_REASON=""
				    SHIPPING_CHARGES="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:ShippingAmount)}"
				    COD_CHARGES=""
				    LEASE_FEES=""
				    SEF_TOTAL=""
				    OTHER_FEES=""
				    GST_HST=""
				    PST=""
				    FEDERAL_TAX=""
				    STATE_TAX=""
				    PO_NUM_NORM=""
				    TOTALMINUSVAT=""
				    LOCATION_NUM=""
				    COMPANY_NUM="{
				    			   if (data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:SalesChannel/ns2:Code) = 'US_EMC') then 
									'45'
								   else if(xf:RegionName(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID']))='US')then
				                   fn:substring-after(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:SalesChannel/ns2:Code),'US_')


				                   else()
				                   
				                 }"
				    ACT_SHIP_DATE=""
				    EST_DEL_DATE_AT_SHIP=""
				    REV_EST_DEL_DATE=""
				    REV_EST_SHIP_DATE=""
					REV_MIN_EST_DEL_DATE="{if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:Fulfillment/ns2:RevisedDeliveryDateTimeMin)!='')then
                                                          (fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xf:TimeZoneConversion(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:Fulfillment/ns2:RevisedDeliveryDateTimeMin),'PT0H'))))
                                                          else()}"
				    REDD_REV_COUNT=""
				    SHIP_METHOD="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:ModeOfTransportCode[@listID='MODE_OF_TRANSPORT_CODE'])}"
				    ACTUAL_METHOD=""
				    TAX_RATE=""
				    ORDER_DISCOUNT="{
				                     let $Amounts :=  ($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleAllowance/ns6:Allowance/ns6:Amount)

                                                                                   
				                      return
										fn-bea:decimal-round(xs:decimal(fn:sum($Amounts)), 10)
                                     
				                     }"
				    GOLD_ACCOUNT_FLAG=""
				    DPS_TYPE=""
				    PREPAY_AMT=""
				    CANCEL_CODE=""
				    RR_DATE=""
                                    RR_PROCESS_FLAG=""

				    CUSTOMER_CLASS=""
				    ORIGINAL_ORDER_REF_NUM = "{if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderProcessingCode[@listID="ORDER_PROCESSING_CODE"])=('C','D') 
									and data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUMBER_CREDIT'])!='')
									then data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUMBER_CREDIT']) 
									
									else if (data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderProcessingCode[@listID="ORDER_PROCESSING_CODE"])='X' and  xf:RegionName(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID']))!='US'
									 and data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUM'])!='')
									 then
									 data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUM'])
									  else if (data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderProcessingCode[@listID="ORDER_PROCESSING_CODE"])=('O','X') and  xf:RegionName(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID']))='US'
									 and data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUM'])!='')
									 then
									 data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUM'])
										
									 else if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUMBER'])!='')
									   then
									    data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUMBER'])
									    
									 else if (data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUM'])!='') 
									  then
									  data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGINAL_ORDER_NUM'])
									 
									 else if (fn:not(fn:upper-case(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderType)) = ('US INVOICE','US INVOICE AND ENTITLEMENT','US INVOICE CORRECTION')))
									  then
									  data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORIGIN_SYSTEM_REFERENCE'])  	 
									
									else()  						     
									}"
                                    DPS_NUM = "{ data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='DPS_NUMBER']) }"
                                    ORDER_DATE = "{ if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:OrderDateTime)!='')then
                                                       (fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xf:TimeZoneConversion(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:OrderDateTime),'PT0H'))))
                                                       else()}"
                                    IR_NUM = "{ data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='IRN_NUMBER']) }"

                                    				 fn:substring-after(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:SalesChannel/ns2:Code[@listID='SALES_CHANNEL_CODE']),'US_')


                                    				 else(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:SalesChannel/ns2:Code[@listID='SALES_CHANNEL_CODE']))
                                    				  }"
                                    SALES_REP_NUM = "{ data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderSalesCommission/ns6:SalesCommission/ns6:SalespersonPartyReference/ns6:PartyIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='SALESREP_NUMBER']) }"
                                    STATUS_DATE = "{if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:RevisionHistory/ns2:CreationDateTime)!='')then
                                                      (fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xf:TimeZoneConversion(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:RevisionHistory/ns2:CreationDateTime),'PT0H'))))
                                                      else()}"
                                    SALES_REP_NAME = "{ data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderSalesCommission/ns6:SalesCommission/ns6:SalespersonPartyReference/ns6:PersonName/ns6:FullName[@languageCode='EN']) }"
                                    ORDER_TYPE = "{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:TypeName)}"
                                    CURRENCY_CD = "{ data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:CurrencyCode[@listID='ISO_CURRENCY_CODE']) }"
                                    CURRENT_STATUS = "{(abacus-xq-fn:LookupDVM("STATUS_CODE","OMAR",data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Status/ns6:Code[@listID='ORDER_STATUS_CODE']),"JDOMS"," "))}"
                                    EST_DEL_DATE = "{ if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:PromisedDeliveryDateTime)!='')then
                                                          (fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xf:TimeZoneConversion(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:PromisedDeliveryDateTime),'PT0H'))))
                                                          else if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:RequestedDeliveryDateTime)!='')then
                                                                (fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xf:TimeZoneConversion(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:RequestedDeliveryDateTime),'PT0H'))))
                                                                else()}"
                                    ORDER_TOTAL = "{ data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:TotalAmount) }"
                                    VAT = "{ data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:TaxAmount) }"
                                    COUNTRY_NUM = "{ data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='IBU_CODE']) }"

                                                        else()}"
                                    QUOTE_NBR = "{ if(xf:RegionName(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID']))='US') then 
												    data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:SourceDocumentReference/ns6:DocumentIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='QUOTE_NUMBER']) 
												    else 
												    data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:SourceDocumentReference/ns6:DocumentIdentification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='SOURCE_QUOTE_NUMBER']) }"
                                    DESTINATION_CODE = ""
                                    AGREEMENT_ID="{if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns6:EBMHeader/ROUTING_PARAMETERS/RoutingParameter[@name="AGREEMENT_ID"])='null') then ''
									else
									data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns6:EBMHeader/ROUTING_PARAMETERS/RoutingParameter[@name="AGREEMENT_ID"])}"
                                    AMF_ORDER_NUM=""
                                    FLEX_BILLING_CODE="{if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:TypeName)='US Flex Billing')
									                       then
									                        'B'
									                       else()}"
                                         				   BILL_FROM_STATE="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:Fulfillment/ns2:ShipFromStateCode)}"

MABD="{ if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:MustDeliverByDateTime)!='')then
  		(
            if(not(((data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:MustDeliverByDateTime))='1-01-01T00:00:00') or ((fn:contains(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:MustDeliverByDateTime),'1-01-02T00:00:00'))))) then	
  			(								
  				if (fn:contains(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:MustDeliverByDateTime),'T')) then									   
									   
					fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xf:TimeZoneConversion(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:MustDeliverByDateTime),'PT0H'))) 
                                                                  
				else(
		
					fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xf:TimeZoneConversion(fn:replace(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:MustDeliverByDateTime),' ','T'),'PT0H')))
					
					)											 
                
			)
			
			else()
		
		)
		else()
      }"

                                        PARTIAL_RETURN_FLAG="{ if(upper-case(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:FullPartialCredit))='FULL')then
                                        						  'N'
                                    	                   else if(upper-case(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:FullPartialCredit))='PARTIAL') then
                                    	    					  'Y'
                                    	                   else()}" 



                                      />

					    RETAIL_FLG="{if($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:ResellerPartyReference/ns6:CustomerPartyAccountTypeCode!='' and data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:ResellerPartyReference/ns6:CustomerPartyAccountTypeCode)!='N')then
					                          data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:ResellerPartyReference/ns6:CustomerPartyAccountTypeCode)
					                 else()}"
					    SEQ_NUM = "{ if(xf:RegionName(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID']))='US')
										then
										fn:substring(fn-bea:trim(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:ResellerPartyReference/ns6:LocationReference/ns6:Address/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='CAM_LOCATION_ID'])),3) 
										else
										data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:ResellerPartyReference/ns6:LocationReference/ns6:Address/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ADDRESS_ID']) 
								     }"
					    MIDDLE_INTIAL="">
					    
                                        </ns0:SalesOrderCustomerDetails>
									else()
                           }    
                </ns0:SalesOrderCustomer>
                <ns0:SalesOrderNote>
				{ 
				if (fn:contains(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:TypeName),'Invoice Correction')) then 
				
                <ns0:OrderNote   NOTE_ID = "1"
                                 NOTE_TYPE = "INV_CORR"  
					             NOTE="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:ShippingInstructions[1])}"/>
 
                else()
                }
                            <ns0:OrderNote   NOTE_ID = "1"
                                             NOTE_TYPE = "SHIP_INSTR"

                                             NOTE_TYPE = "CUST_SVC_INSTR"
                                             NOTE = "{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:Fulfillment/ns2:InstallationNote/ns6:Content)}"  />

                                             NOTE_TYPE = "SPEC_INSTR"
                                             NOTE = "{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:Note/ns6:Content)}"  />
                </ns0:SalesOrderNote>
                <ns0:SalesOrderLineItem>
                { 
                if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID'])!=11)
                 then
                 for  $SalesOrderLines at $lineCntr in ($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine)
                  return
				   let $custom := $SalesOrderLines/ns10:Custom
				   for $Manufacturing at $partCntr in $custom/ns3:ManufacturingItem
				   where $custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemManufacturingCharacteristics/ns8:ConfiguratorModelTypeCode ='STANDARD'
				   return 
                  <ns0:LineItems LINE_ID = "{ if(fn:contains(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderSource),'MNA') or fn:contains(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderSource),'BULKLOAD')) then 
                  						 fn:concat(data($lineCntr),data($partCntr))
                  						else(data($Manufacturing/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='DETAIL_SEQ_NUM'])
                  						 )}"
                                   TIE_NUM = "{ data($SalesOrderLines/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_TIE_NUMBER']) }"
                                   MODEL_NUM = "{ data($custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemManufacturingCharacteristics/ns6:BaseModelItemReference/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='MODEL_ID']) }"
                                   SKU_NUM = "{ data($custom/ns3:Item/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ITEM_NUMBER']) }"
                                   DESCRIPTION = "{if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID'])='3535')then 
                                                   ( if (data($custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Description[@languageCode='JA']))then
                                                     (data($custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Description[@languageCode='JA']))
                                                     else(data($custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Description[@languageCode='EN'])))
                                                     else(data($custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Description[@languageCode='EN'])) }"
                                   QTY_ORD = "{ if(fn:contains(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:TypeName),"Credit"))then

                                                else(data($SalesOrderLines/ns10:OrderQuantity)) }"
                                   QTY_SHIPPED=""

                                   CFI_COMMENTS=""
				   LEAD_TIME=""
				   EOL = "{ if(data($custom/ns3:Item/ns6:EffectiveTimePeriod/ns6:EndDateTime)!='')then
				             (fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xf:TimeZoneConversion(data($custom/ns3:Item/ns6:EffectiveTimePeriod/ns6:EndDateTime),'PT0H'))))
				             else()}"
                                   CFI_NUM = "{ data($custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Custom/ns9:SystemIntegratorIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='SI_NUMBER']) }"
                                   SYS_FLAG = "{ if(data($Manufacturing/ns8:ItemManufacturingCharacteristics/ns8:InventoryAssetIndicator)='true')then
                                                 'Y'
                                                 else('N') }"
			       			       EXT_PRICE=""
                                   CONTRACT_START_DATE = "{ fn-bea:date-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy",data($custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyStartDateTime)) }"
                                   CONTRACT_END_DATE = "{ fn-bea:date-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy",data($custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyEndDateTime)) }"

                                   SERVICE_FLAG = "{ if(data($custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ServiceIndicator)='true')then
                                                      'Y'
                                                      else('N') }"
                                   PART_NUM = "{ data($Manufacturing/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='PART_NUMBER']) }"
				   PART_DESCRIPTION="{data($Manufacturing/ns8:Name[@languageCode='EN'])}"
                                   LIST_PRICE = "{ data($SalesOrderLines/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns6:UnitListPrice/ns6:Amount) }"
				   DESTINATION_CODE=""
				   ITEM_CLASS=""
				   GLOBAL_IDENTIFIER="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom[ns3:ManufacturingItem=$Manufacturing]/ns3:globalIdentifier)}"                                   
				   DURATION_MONTHS ="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom[ns3:ManufacturingItem=$Manufacturing]/ns3:DurationInMonths)}"
				   DURATION_DAYS="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom[ns3:ManufacturingItem=$Manufacturing]/ns3:durationInDays)}"/>
                      else(
                      

						
						
						for $OrderTieNumber in distinct-values($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_TIE_NUMBER'])
						let $SKU := $SalesOrderLine[ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_TIE_NUMBER']=$OrderTieNumber and ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemManufacturingCharacteristics/ns8:ConfiguratorModelTypeCode ='STANDARD' and ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom/ns3:Cancelled_Flag='N' and ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom/ns3:IsFreightSKU='N' ]
						for  $LineCntr in 1 to fn:count($SKU) 
					    return
				                      
				  
				                   <ns0:LineItems LINE_ID = "{ data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:seq)}"
                                   TIE_NUM = "{ data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_TIE_NUMBER']) }"
                                   MODEL_NUM = "{ data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemManufacturingCharacteristics/ns6:BaseModelItemReference/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='MODEL_ID']) }"
                                   SKU_NUM = "{ data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ITEM_NUMBER']) }"
                                   DESCRIPTION = "{if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID'])='3535')then 
                                                   ( if (data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Description[@languageCode='JA']))then
                                                     (data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Description[@languageCode='JA']))
                                                     else(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Description[@languageCode='EN'])))
                                                     else(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Description[@languageCode='EN'])) }"
                                   QTY_ORD = "{ if(fn:contains(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:TypeName),"Credit"))then
                                                (xs:string(fn:concat("-",data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:OrderQuantity))))
                                                else(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:OrderQuantity)) }"
                                   QTY_SHIPPED=""
				   UNIT_PRICE = "{ data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns6:UnitSalePrice/ns6:Amount) }"
                                   SVC_TAG = "{ data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:ManufacturerItemID[@schemeID='MANUAL_SERVICE_TAG']) }"
                                   CFI_COMMENTS=""
				   LEAD_TIME=""
				   EOL = "{ if(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns6:EffectiveTimePeriod/ns6:EndDateTime)!='')then
				             (fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",fn:adjust-dateTime-to-timezone(xf:TimeZoneConversion(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns6:EffectiveTimePeriod/ns6:EndDateTime),'PT0H'))))
				             else()}"
                                   CFI_NUM = "{ data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Custom/ns9:SystemIntegratorIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='SI_NUMBER']) }"
                                   SYS_FLAG = "{ if(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:InventoryAssetIndicator)='true')then
                                                 'Y'
                                                 else('N') }"
			           EXT_PRICE=""
                                   CONTRACT_START_DATE = "{ let $strlen := fn:string-length(fn:string(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyStartDateTime)))
                                   							return 
								   if(data($strlen) > 11) then
                                   (fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyStartDateTime)))
                                    else if(data($strlen) = 11 or (data($strlen) = 10 and fn:string-length(fn:substring-before($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyStartDateTime,'-')) = 1)) then
                                   (                                 
								   let $warrantyStartDate := tokenize(fn:string(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyStartDateTime)),"-")  
                                   let $day := $warrantyStartDate[1]
								   let $month := xf:MonthConversion(fn:upper-case($warrantyStartDate[2]))
								   let $year := $warrantyStartDate[3]
                                   return fn:concat($day,"/",$month,"/",$year)
                                   )
								   else if (data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyStartDateTime) = '1-JAN-1') then 
								   "01/01/0001"
                                   else
                                    (fn-bea:date-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy",data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyStartDateTime)))}"
                                   CONTRACT_END_DATE = "{ let $strlen := fn:string-length(fn:string(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyEndDateTime)))
								   						return
								   if(data($strlen) > 11) then
                                   (fn-bea:dateTime-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm:ss",data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyEndDateTime)))
                                   else if(data($strlen) = 11 or (data($strlen) = 10 and fn:string-length(fn:substring-before($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyEndDateTime,'-')) = 1)) then
                                   (                                 
								   let $warrantyStartDate := tokenize(fn:string(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyEndDateTime)), "-")  
                                   let $day := $warrantyStartDate[1]
								   let $month := xf:MonthConversion(fn:upper-case($warrantyStartDate[2]))
								   let $year := $warrantyStartDate[3]
                                   return fn:concat($day,"/",$month,"/",$year)
                                   )
								   else if (data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyEndDateTime) = '1-JAN-1') then 
								   "01/01/0001"
								   else
                                    (fn-bea:date-to-string-with-format("dd/MM/yyyy",data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemServiceCharacteristics/ns8:Custom/ns9:WarrantyEndDateTime)))}"
				                   BILL_CYCLE_CODE = "{if( fn:exists($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:BillCadence) and data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:BillCadence)!='')
														then
														(abacus-xq-fn:LookupDVM("BILL_CYCLE_CODE","OMAR",data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:BillCadence),"SODS"," "))
														else("")}"
                                   SERVICE_FLAG = "{ if(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ServiceIndicator)='true')then
                                                      'Y'
                                                      else('N') }"
                                   PART_NUM = "{ $SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:DellMfgPartNum[@schemeID='DELL_PART_NUMBER']}"
								   PART_DESCRIPTION="{data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:Name[@languageCode='EN'])}"
				                                   LIST_PRICE = "{ data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns6:UnitListPrice/ns6:Amount) }"
								   DESTINATION_CODE=""
								   ITEM_CLASS=""
								   TAXABLE_FLAG="{if(data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:TaxOverRideFlag)='E')then
				                                                      'N'
				                                                      else('Y')}"
				                   GLOBAL_IDENTIFIER="{data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:globalIdentifier)}"                                   
				                   DURATION_MONTHS ="{data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:DurationInMonths)}"
				                   DURATION_DAYS="{data($SKU[$LineCntr]/ns10:SalesOrderLine//ns10:Custom/ns3:durationInDays)}"
				                   
				                   />)                                 
				                      
                 }
                </ns0:SalesOrderLineItem>
                <ns0:SalesOrderPaymentInfo>
                {
                if(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:BusinessUnitReference/ns6:BusinessUnitIdentification/ns6:ID[@schemeID='GLOBAL_BU_ID'])!=11)
                 then
                 <ns0:PaymentInfo PAYMENT_TERM  ="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:PaymentTerm/ns6:Code[@listID='PAYMENT_TERM_CODE'])}"
		                  PAYCODE=""
				  DESCRIPTION="{data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns6:PaymentTerm/ns6:Description)}"
				  AMOUNT=""
				  CARD_NUM=""
				  EXP_DATE=""
				  AUTH=""
				  CURRENCY_CD=""
				  CARD_TYPE=""
				  FUND_SRC_REQD_FLG=""
				  CREDIT_CARD_USED_FLG=""/>
				  else(let $MultiPaymentTerms := $publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns2:MultiplePaymentTerms
				            for $Payments in ($MultiPaymentTerms)
				            return
				                <ns0:PaymentInfo PAYCODE = "{ if (data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderTypePayCode)!='') then
				                                                 data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderTypePayCode)
				                                                   else if ((not(fn:exists($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderTypePayCode)) or data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:OrderTypePayCode)='') and data($Payments/ns2:CardType[1])='')
																   then
																   data($Payments/ns2:PayCode[1])
																   else("") 
																   }"
                                     DESCRIPTION = "{ data($Payments/ns2:Name[1]) }"
                                     AMOUNT = "{ xs:double($Payments/ns2:Amount[1]) }"
                                     CARD_NUM = ""
                                     EXP_DATE = ""
                                     AUTH = ""
                                     CURRENCY_CD = ""
                                     CARD_TYPE = "{ data($Payments/ns2:CardType[1])}"
                                     PAYMENT_TERM = "{ data($Payments/ns2:Name[1]) }"
                                     FUND_SRC_REQD_FLG = ""
                                     CREDIT_CARD_USED_FLG = ""
                                     IBU_AMOUNT=
                                     "{ let $USDtoLocalCurrencyRate:=data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:Custom/ns3:USDtoLocalCurrencyRate)
                                       return
                                     (xs:double($USDtoLocalCurrencyRate)*(xs:double($Payments/ns2:Amount[1])))}"/>)				 
               } </ns0:SalesOrderPaymentInfo>
                <ns0:SalesOrderTax>
               {		
					let $distinctTaxTypeCodes :=  distinct-values(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine[ns10:Custom[ns3:Cancelled_Flag='N']/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemManufacturingCharacteristics/ns8:ConfiguratorModelTypeCode ='STANDARD']/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule[1]/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleTax/ns6:Tax/ns6:Code[@listID='TAX_AUTHORITY_TYPE']))
					for $TaxType in $distinctTaxTypeCodes
					return
					<ns0:OrderTax TAX_TYPE_CODE = "{let $TaxTypeCode := data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine[ns10:Custom/ns3:Cancelled_Flag='N']/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule[1]/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleTax/ns6:Tax[ns6:Code=$TaxType]/ns6:Code[@listID='TAX_TYPE_CODE']) 
					                                return
					                                $TaxTypeCode[1]}"
					              AUTHORITY_TYPE= "{ data($TaxType)}"
					              TAX_IBU_AMT="{	let $SkuCurrencyCode:=data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:TotalAmount/@currencyCode)
					                            return
					                           let $TIA:=fn:round-half-to-even(xf:SkuCurrencyConvert($TransectionCurrencyCode,$SkuCurrencyCode,xs:decimal(sum(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine[ns10:Custom/ns3:Cancelled_Flag='N']/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleTax/ns6:Tax[ns6:Code=$TaxType]/ns6:Amount))),$USDtoSellingCurrencyRate,$USDtoLocalCurrencyRate),2)
					                           return
					                           $TIA}"
					                            
		                          TAX_TRAN_AMT = "{let $TTA:=fn:round-half-to-even(xs:decimal(sum($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine[ns10:Custom/ns3:Cancelled_Flag='N']/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleTax/ns6:Tax[ns6:Code=$TaxType]/ns6:Amount)),2)
												  return
												  $TTA }"
		                          />
		          }
			</ns0:SalesOrderTax>
			<ns0:SalesOrderLineTax>
			{
                        
						
						for $OrderTieNumberTax in distinct-values($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_TIE_NUMBER'])
						let $SKUT := $SalesOrderLine[ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_TIE_NUMBER']=$OrderTieNumberTax and ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns8:ItemManufacturingCharacteristics/ns8:ConfiguratorModelTypeCode ='STANDARD' and ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom/ns3:Cancelled_Flag='N' and ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom/ns3:IsFreightSKU='N' ]
						
						for  $LineCntrT in 1 to fn:count($SKUT) 
						let $distinctTaxTypeCodes := distinct-values(data($SKUT[$LineCntrT]/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleTax/ns6:Tax/ns6:Code[@listID='TAX_AUTHORITY_TYPE']))
					    for $TaxType in $distinctTaxTypeCodes
					    return            
            <ns0:LineTax LINE_ID="{ data($SKUT[$LineCntrT]/ns10:seq)}"
             TAX_TYPE_CODE="{let $TaxTypeCode := data($SKUT[$LineCntrT]/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleTax/ns6:Tax[ns6:Code=$TaxType]/ns6:Code[@listID='TAX_TYPE_CODE']) return
					                                $TaxTypeCode[1]}"
			 AUTHORITY_TYPE= "{ data($TaxType)}"
			TAX_IBU_AMT="{let $SkuCurrencyCode := data($SKUT[$LineCntrT]/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns6:UnitSalePrice/ns6:Amount/@currencyCode)
						   
					       return			
							
					       let $TAIA:= xf:SkuCurrencyConvert($TransectionCurrencyCode,$SkuCurrencyCode,xs:decimal(sum(data($SKUT[$LineCntrT]/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleTax/ns6:Tax[ns6:Code=$TaxType]/ns6:Amount))),$USDtoSellingCurrencyRate,$USDtoLocalCurrencyRate)
					       return
					      fn:round-half-to-even(xs:decimal($TAIA),2)}"   
			 TAX_TRAN_AMT="{ let $TTAMT := xs:decimal(sum(data($SKUT[$LineCntrT]/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleTax/ns6:Tax[ns6:Code=$TaxType]/ns6:Amount)))
			                 return
			                 fn:round-half-to-even(xs:decimal($TTAMT),2)}" 
	                         
	                         
			  TAX_RATE="{let $TR:= xs:decimal(sum(data($SKUT[$LineCntrT]/ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:SalesOrderSchedule/ns10:SalesOrderScheduleTax/ns6:Tax[ns6:Code=$TaxType]/ns6:TaxRate)))
                             return
			                 fn:round-half-to-even(xs:decimal($TR),2)}" />
			}
			</ns0:SalesOrderLineTax>
			<ns0:ServiceTags>
			{
			if((upper-case(data($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:FullPartialCredit))='PARTIAL') and 
			(fn:exists($publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine[ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:ManufacturerItemID[@schemeID="SERVICE_TAG"]])))
			then
			(			
			let $ServicetagSalesOrderLines := $publishSalesOrderEBM1/ns10:DataArea/ns10:PublishSalesOrder/ns10:SalesOrderLine[ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:ManufacturerItemID[@schemeID="SERVICE_TAG"]]
			for $ServicetagSalesOrderLine in $ServicetagSalesOrderLines
			let $TieNumber := $ServicetagSalesOrderLine/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_TIE_NUMBER']
			let $BaseSku := $SalesOrderLine[ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns6:Identification/ns6:AlternateObjectKey/ns6:ID[@schemeID='ORDER_TIE_NUMBER'] = $TieNumber and ns10:SalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom/ns3:InventoryAssetIndicator[fn:lower-case(text())='true']]
			for $ManufacturerItemID in  $ServicetagSalesOrderLine/ns10:Custom/ns3:Item/ns6:ItemIdentification/ns6:ManufacturerItemID[@schemeID='SERVICE_TAG']
		    return 
			<ns0:ServiceTag LINE_ID="{data($BaseSku/ns10:seq)}"
							TYPE="SVC_TAG"
							SVC_TAG="{data($ManufacturerItemID)}"/>	
			)
			else()
			}			
			</ns0:ServiceTags>
            </ns0:CreateOrder>
}
        </ns0:CreateSODSOrder>
};
